    </div>
</div>
<div class="content-body" style="margin-top:10px;">
    <div class="content-header">
        <div>
            <h4 class="content-title content-title-sm">
                <b style="background-image: linear-gradient(to right, rgb(255,103,43), rgb(223,15,105));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    color: transparent;">插件市场</b>
            </h4>
            <span>无所不有的插件市场 🛒💨💨💨</span>
            <p></p>
            <div class="systemPluginBox">
                <b><i data-feather="settings" style="width:18px;"></i> 系统插件选装</b>
                <p></p>
                <div style="display: flex; gap: 10px;">
                    <label><input type="checkbox" name="options" class="systemPlugins" value="use_dalle3_withpr"> DALL-E3绘画</label>
                    <i data-feather="help-circle" style="width:18px;cursor:pointer" onclick="dalleinfo()" data-toggle="tooltip" title="当您安装此插件，您可以在【创意工坊对话】中，描述您的【绘画要求】，插件会根据您的语义选择调用时机"></i>
                    <label><input type="checkbox" name="options" class="systemPlugins" value="search_google_when_gpt_cannot_answer"> 谷歌搜索</label>
                    <i data-feather="help-circle" style="width:18px;cursor:pointer" onclick="googlesearchinfo()" data-toggle="tooltip" title="当您安装此插件，您可以在【创意工坊对话】中，要求AI进行【谷歌搜索】，适用于工坊中所有AI模型"></i>
                    <label><input type="checkbox" name="options" class="systemPlugins" value="search_knowledge_base"> 知识库检索</label>
                    <i data-feather="help-circle" style="width:18px;cursor:pointer" onclick="knowledgeinfo()" data-toggle="tooltip" title="当您安装此插件，您可以在【知识库对话】中，令AI查询您的【私有知识库】，如【未安装】此插件，您将【无法使用知识库对话】"></i>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content-main text-center">
        <div class="header-search mb-4">
            <i data-feather="search"></i>
            <input type="search" class="form-control" placeholder="输入插件名搜索插件，回车搜索" id="searchKey" style="width: 100%;">
        </div>
        <div class="row" id="masonry-layout">
            <li class="divider-text">
                加载中...
            </li>
